{"article_id":"tYcC69EX0zKh1DlL","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Attorney general nominee William Barr will pledge this week to allow special counsel Robert Mueller to complete his investigation into suspected collusion between President Donald Trump ' s 2016 campaign and Russia ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"according to his written testimony","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"submitted to the Senate .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"The Mueller investigation is expected to take center stage","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"when Barr appears before the Senate Judiciary Committee for his confirmation hearing Tuesday and Wednesday .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"In his prepared testimony , Barr emphasized his respect for the investigation","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"and aimed to reassure lawmakers","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that his allegiance is to the rule of law .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"\" I believe","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"it is in the best interest of everyone","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"- the President , Congress , and most importantly , the American people -","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"that this matter be resolved","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"by allowing the Special Counsel to complete his work , \"","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Barr wrote in his testimony .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"\" The country needs a credible resolution of these issues . \"","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"Barr has faced criticism since his nomination last month","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"because of a series of published comments critical of both the Russia probe and Mueller ' s interest","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"in investigating","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"whether Trump obstructed justice","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"when he fired FBI Director James Comey .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"But in his written testimony , Barr sought to deflect that criticism","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"by noting","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"he has known Mueller \" personally and professionally \" for 30 years ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"dating back to their time","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"working together during the George H.W Bush administration ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"when Barr was serving as attorney general .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"\" We ' ve been friends since , \"","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"Barr said .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"\" I have the utmost respect for Bob and his distinguished record of public service . \"","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Playbook newsletter","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"Sign up today","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"to receive the # 1-rated newsletter in politics","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"Email Sign Up","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"By signing up","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"you agree to receive email newsletters or alerts from .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"You can unsubscribe at any time .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"and the Google Privacy Policy and Terms of Service apply .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"Mueller ' s 20-month-old probe has no deadline","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"but is widely viewed as being in its closing stages .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"In his written testimony , Barr alluded to the special counsel ' s \" public actions to date \" as a signal","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"that he too thinks","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"Mueller \" is well along in his investigation . \"","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"If confirmed ,","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Barr will have authority over all major decision points in the Mueller probe , from Mueller 's budget to subpoenas and criminal indictments .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"The attorney general also has the final say","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"in determining whether to release publicly Mueller ' s final report ,","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"which under DOJ regulations has a limited mandate","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"requiring him to explain only who he has prosecuted and who he declined to prosecute .","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"Pre-emptively addressing questions","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"about whether Barr would allow Mueller ' s report to be made public ,","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"the attorney general nominee vowed ,","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"\" My goal will be to provide as much transparency","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"as I can","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"consistent with the law . \"","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"In his prepared testimony , Barr also signaled","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"that Mueller ' s report might cover a far wider breadth of topics","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"that have been under investigation .","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"Barr is in line","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"to replace former Attorney General Jeff Sessions ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"who faced withering criticism from Trump","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"that he wasn ' t doing enough","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"to protect the president from the Mueller probe .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"Trump nominated Barr in December","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"to succeed Sessions .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Anticipating senators ' questions about the president ' s well-stated concerns ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"Barr pledged","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"if he ' s confirmed","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"he \" will not permit partisan politics , personal interests , or any other improper consideration to interfere with this or any other investigation . \"","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"\" I will follow the Special Counsel regulations scrupulously and in good faith ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"and on my watch , Bob","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"[ Mueller ]","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"will be allowed to complete his work , \"","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"Barr said in his prepared testimony .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"Barr 's promise","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"to allow Mueller to complete his investigation","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"is likely to provide some relief to lawmakers ,","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"even if it puts him in the crosshairs of Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"who has routinely criticized the Mueller 's probe as a \" witch hunt . \"","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Sen. Chris Coons","depth":14},{"id":81,"text":"( D-Del . )","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"told reporters","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"that he was `` very encouraged '' by Barr 's prepared statement","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"but added","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"that he had several outstanding questions .","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"Among those questions are whether Barr would submit to an ethics review","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"to determine","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"whether he should recuse himself from overseeing the investigation ,","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"what his views of pardons are","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"and whether he would defend legislation","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"to protect Mueller","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"if it passed Congress .","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"Last week , Senate Judiciary Chairman Lindsey Graham","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"( R-S.C. ) ,","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"along with Coons and Sens . Thom Tillis","depth":15},{"id":96,"text":"( R-N.C. )","depth":15},{"id":97,"text":"and Cory Booker","depth":15},{"id":98,"text":"( D-N.J. ) ,","depth":15},{"id":99,"text":"introduced legislation","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"to clarify","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"that the special counsel may only be fired by a senior Department of Justice official for good cause .","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"The legislation gives a special counsel 10 days","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"to request judicial review of his or her firing .","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"Senate Democrats are also expected to grill Barr on a memo","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"he wrote last year to Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"that described Mueller ' s investigation into possible obstruction of justice by Trump as \" fatally misconceived . \"","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"In his written testimony , Barr described the controversial memo as \" narrow in scope \"","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"and emphasized","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"that it \" did not address","depth":15},{"id":110,"text":"- or in any way question -","depth":15},{"id":111,"text":"the Special Counsel ' s core investigation into Russian interference in the 2016 election. \"","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"He added","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"that memo did not suggest","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"that a president could never be guilty of obstruction of justice .","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"Sen. Chuck Grassley","depth":14},{"id":116,"text":"( R-Iowa ) ,","depth":14},{"id":117,"text":"who chaired the Judiciary Committee in the last Congress ,","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"described Barr 's statements on Mueller as `` pretty significant . ''","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"But","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"while Barr addressed the Mueller investigation head-on ,","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"his opening remarks were not enough","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"to ease concerns from some Democrats on the Judiciary Committee .","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"Sen. Sheldon Whitehouse","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"( D-R.I. )","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"said","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"that his opening statement was `` well-written ''","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"but left several questions unanswered .","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"Whitehouse plans to ask Barr about his contact with the Trump administration about the special counsel investigation before his nomination ,","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"according to a letter to Barr","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"released Monday .","depth":14},{"id":131,"text":"`` His remarks still fail to provide the kind of very specific iron clad commitment","depth":15},{"id":132,"text":"that I think","depth":17},{"id":133,"text":"is necessary","depth":17},{"id":134,"text":"to protect the special counsel from political interference","depth":17},{"id":135,"text":"and enable the investigation to be completed , ''","depth":17},{"id":136,"text":"said Sen. Richard Blumenthal","depth":16},{"id":137,"text":"( D-Conn. ) ,","depth":16},{"id":138,"text":"who added","depth":16},{"id":139,"text":"that `` he never says","depth":17},{"id":140,"text":"that he will resist the president","depth":18},{"id":141,"text":"if he 's ordered by the president to stop the investigation . ''","depth":18},{"id":142,"text":"Blumenthal said","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"that among the commitments","depth":16},{"id":144,"text":"he would like to see from Barr on Tuesday","depth":16},{"id":145,"text":"are that he will stand up to Trump ,","depth":16},{"id":146,"text":"allow for the enforcement of subpoenas","depth":17},{"id":147,"text":"and ensure","depth":18},{"id":148,"text":"that the special counsel 's budget is sustained and increased .","depth":18},{"id":149,"text":"In addition to addressing the Mueller investigation ,","depth":6},{"id":150,"text":"Barr pledged to implement the newcriminal justice reform law , enforce immigration laws","depth":7},{"id":151,"text":"and to prioritize fighting foreign interference in U.S. elections .","depth":7},{"id":152,"text":"Barr is expected to receive broad Republican support .","depth":2},{"id":153,"text":"But he ' s already come under scrutiny from some Senate Democrats on the committee ,","depth":3},{"id":154,"text":"who have said","depth":4},{"id":155,"text":"he should have reached out to their offices","depth":5},{"id":156,"text":"to meet prior to the confirmation hearings .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":313,"left":308,"right":312,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":308,"left":185,"right":307,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":171,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nu